        public com.google.api.ads.adwords.jaxws.v201809.cm.Selector build()
        Description copied from interface: SelectorBuilderInterface
        Builds a new Selector.

        When a Selector is built by this method, the state of the builder doesn't change. If you need to clean the builder, the best way to do it, is by creating a new instance.

        Specified by:
        build in interface SelectorBuilderInterface<com.google.api.ads.adwords.jaxws.v201809.cm.Selector>
        Returns:
        the new Selector containing all the configuration that was set previously.
